text: Amblymora carinipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1974. It is known from the Celebes Islands.BioLib.cz - Amblymora carinipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1974
title: Amblymora carinipennis
